45 Barbarian Shaman 
Valiant Crusaders</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ushamanpimp.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shamanpimp</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(7/4/02 5:14:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2717.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spirit of the Cheetah (not a topic about whose faster)</span><hr size=1> it used to be useful for when it refreshed on zoning.  i used to mem it back in the day when mistmoore and unrest had 50+ people in it. its useful if youre within zone line range... but if you arent, its of little use since things will catch up to you when it runs out and sow wears off. <p>_____________________________<BR>
